{"tid":258901,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解依家YouTube幾乎都係Vlog？","createTime":"2017-05-26T13:25:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T13:28:17.000Z","uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b85a894b2e36b608ed6b1e616a90e265ca9e06b9","tid":258901,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:25:53.000Z","msg":"我個感受好似Smosh咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=llJhUlGNIJ4&amp;t=8s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DllJhUlGNIJ4%26t%3D8s&d=EkSOzQ7ZVjnG5t8dBASUigRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=2432b559\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=llJhUlGNIJ4&amp;t=8s</a><br />\n<br />\n我唔中意Vloger係因為佢比一般Youtuber更偶像化<br />\n<br />\n就算你話笑波子、大J、寶欣好柒，但人地打機就打機，食野就食野（依家應該轉晒行做Vlog），你唔排除可能真係有人欣賞佢地呢方面做嘅野<br />\n<br />\n但係Vlog，今日睇下佢買衫；聽日睇下佢去旅行；後日睇下佢玩手指陀螺，啲片平均都冇咩內容，依家Youtube算法仲要推咗好多呢啲片上嚟<br />\n<br />\n最慘Vlog有傳染性，咁搞法Youtube遲早變晒做個人Blog"},{"pid":"ffa73440572bbc3aee5304535ad13c305fef24fc","tid":258901,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:28:17.000Z","msg":"大J都係Vlog，冇睇過佢唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Sorry"}]}